    "MissionGiver": "XenoThreat",
    "Title": "Repossess Supplies",
    "Description": "As much as XenoThreat has strived to make Pyro a pure haven for Humans, not everyone is aligned with our goals. Chief among them is the Headhunters, who have debased themselves by hiring an alien hauler to deliver supplies to them. We missed the chance to hit that shipment, but still want to send the message that working with aliens in any capacity will not be tolerated in this system. \n\nThat shipment was delivered to ~mission(Pickup1|Address). We want someone to hit the outpost, claim the ~mission(item), and take it to ~mission(Dropoff1|Address) so we can properly dispose of it. \n\nYou up for keeping Pyro free from alien influence?\n\nComm. Spec. Engler",
    "DisplayDescription": "As much as XenoThreat has strived to make Pyro a pure haven for Humans, not everyone is aligned with our goals. Chief among them is the Headhunters, who have debased themselves by hiring an alien hauler to deliver supplies to them. We missed the chance to hit that shipment, but still want to send the message that working with aliens in any capacity will not be tolerated in this system. \n\nThat shipment was delivered to [Pickup1|Address]. We want someone to hit the outpost, claim the [item], and take it to [Dropoff1|Address] so we can properly dispose of it. \n\nYou up for keeping Pyro free from alien influence?\n\nComm. Spec. Engler",
